These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
City: liverpool, hannover
2 different games are played: snooker, chess
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, sports
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, december
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, egyptian
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, azure
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
2. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| City         | hannover  | liverpool       |
| Game           | chess   | snooker    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | documentary   |
| Birthday   | december      | july     |
| Nationality         | egyptian | canadian      |
| Color     | azure       | grey           |

