.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, sunflower
House: palace, modern
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, snowboarding
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, romance
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, hiking
2 different pets are kept: cat, rat
City: venice, paris
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
6. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Flower      | sunflower         | orchid       |
| House          | palace        | modern |
| Sport           | snowboarding | rugby    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance        | adventure  |
| Hobby   | hiking        | drawing       |
| Pet           | rat            | cat        |
| City     | paris            | venice       |

