.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, balloon-flower
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, video-games
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, september
House: wooden, townhouse
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, alhambra
There 2 different types of food: apple, garlic
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
2. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the wooden house is on the left of the person eating apple##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
5. the alhambra-smoker is the person watching action movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Flower      | balloon-flower    | aconite   |
| Hobby         | video-games | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | sports      | action     |
| Birthday   | september        | august        |
| House           | wooden        | townhouse |
| Cigar         | game    | alhambra |
| Food     | garlic         | apple       |

