3. the software-developer is in an even position##4
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the tower house##3
5. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4
6. the tower house is the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| House      | farmhouse       | tower   |
